{"id": 1603, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得什么样的朋友关系算是铁？", "description": "听说现在流行“很久不见面但就像昨天才刚刚一起喝茶聊天过”的朋友。", "record_count": 9968, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170401105205AGQzuDPTymkZN9er.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-03T17:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 187392, "content": "可以毫无顾虑随时打扰的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912475}, {"id": 187648, "content": "在一起呆着很舒服，需要的时候力挺。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992982}, {"id": 187904, "content": "既可以亲密无间，又可以相忘于江湖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731774}, {"id": 188160, "content": "能在他/她面前做自己！即便撒娇，任性，都不会感到有任何不合适，会包容彼此。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993737}, {"id": 187393, "content": "一张损嘴 一颗真心", "image": null, "praise_count": 558, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992636}, {"id": 187649, "content": "见面后就算有一刻不说话，也一点都不尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928052}, {"id": 187650, "content": "在某个共同患难的时间段会积累下神奇的默契#相视一笑，心照不宣#", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992587}, {"id": 187906, "content": "在一起什么都不说也不会尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993345}, {"id": 188162, "content": "举手投足嬉笑怒骂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333572}, {"id": 188674, "content": "一起走路可以一句话不说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 188930, "content": "看到这个标题时你所想到的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995822}, {"id": 187395, "content": "只有在基督里的弟兄姊妹才是最铁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992639}, {"id": 188163, "content": "多关心 少吹牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993745}, {"id": 188675, "content": "平时不常联系，但生日时总会守着时间祝福；目前为止一年大概能见一次，每次见面都有说不完的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995077}, {"id": 189187, "content": "经常在一起互黑有事一起承担", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996734}, {"id": 190467, "content": "关键时刻靠得住", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001201}, {"id": 187396, "content": "不会和别一再私下议论他的不好，和他在一起不会有贫富的压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992641}, {"id": 187652, "content": "不管做什么都会提前跟我说", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992985}, {"id": 187908, "content": "就算是彼此坐下来玩手机，也不尴尬的朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536152}, {"id": 188164, "content": "一起大保健", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993752}, {"id": 189188, "content": "不刻意\n不猜忌\n不抱怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961332}, {"id": 187397, "content": "不管相隔多远，不管多久没有联系，聊天时的感觉仍若初遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992644}, {"id": 187653, "content": "在对方面前可以做自己，吵着吵着就笑了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992982}, {"id": 187909, "content": "以诚相待", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980809}, {"id": 188165, "content": "不论多久没见 平时也不怎么联络 见面的时候也不会觉得尴尬 聊起来滔滔不绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691416}, {"id": 188933, "content": "骂完你傻但是会出主意的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995844}, {"id": 190725, "content": "也不会顾忌什么见面就瞎聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975122}, {"id": 285190, "content": "第一时间想到的那小伙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732552}, {"id": 187654, "content": "什么都可以说，随时可以找，好久不联系，突然联系一次也不会觉得生疏，彼此之间可以随随便便", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719832}, {"id": 187910, "content": "接到电话就觉得高兴", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993352}, {"id": 188678, "content": "我和徐小轶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973951}, {"id": 187399, "content": "看到标题第一个想到的那个帅小伙～", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 837370}, {"id": 187655, "content": "经常挂在嘴上的，我有个盆友啊他.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900190}, {"id": 189447, "content": "吃饭不说话也不会尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997376}, {"id": 189959, "content": "你的动态我都知道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999263}, {"id": 195079, "content": "有什么困难第一时间无偿帮忙，有什么事能说清楚不含糊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445059}, {"id": 187656, "content": "你就是我，我就是你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721694}, {"id": 188680, "content": "需要她的时候她都在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893846}, {"id": 189960, "content": "各种臭味相投", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 76785}, {"id": 190472, "content": "能被吸铁石吸住？", "image": "img/option/option/20170411104349vgtWjDTuN5OSYQFB", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001223}, {"id": 187401, "content": "无处不在", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991959}, {"id": 187657, "content": "打归打，吵归吵，需要的时候义无反顾伸出援手。", "image": "img/option/option/20170404122434ZFC0QheoEXgrKL7j.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831557}, {"id": 188169, "content": "知乎有相关问题和回答。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993757}, {"id": 188937, "content": "废话一大堆但还是乐此不疲", "image": "img/option/option/20170406145306uFhwBj91I3c5fDVy", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995817}, {"id": 190473, "content": "能被吸铁石吸住？", "image": "img/option/option/20170411104848t5RVjdl3QO1qYTyC", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001223}, {"id": 187402, "content": "想起什么事，抓起电话就打，没事也不找事，说吃饭不问原因就来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992650}, {"id": 187658, "content": "伤心的时候能安慰对方，开心事能和对方一起共享，做错事时大胆批评，很久不见也不伤感，再见时又能畅聊天地，总的来说就是保留了真性情的朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881460}, {"id": 187914, "content": "自己拼命逞强说没事 忍着眼泪和委屈 见到他就哭了", "image": "img/option/option/20170404170320bOmeXEd8Aw6YcNp7", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993362}, {"id": 188682, "content": "ta犯二了，可以直接说：你个sb", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749938}, {"id": 189962, "content": "  一言不合就去蹭吃蹭喝蹭睡她也不会嫌弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999275}]}